snippet: Ian Poulter came from four strokes back to win the tournament in Shenzhen, China, shooting a 7-under 65 for his first title of the year.
abstract: Ian Poulter rallies from four strokes back to win HSBC Champions golf tournament in Shenzhen, China; other golf news noted.

headline.main: Poulter Rallies to Win HSBC Champions
